        "$type": "app.bsky.embed.video",
        "alt": "Script to generate this:\n\n~~~PowerShell\n$TriangleRGBAShift = @{\n        RGBAShift = $true\n        RGBAShiftRedHorizontal=-10\n        RGBAShiftRedVertical=10\n        RGBAShiftGreenHorizontal= 10\n        RGBAShiftGreenVertical= -10        \n        RGBAShiftBlueVertical=10\n    }\n\nEdit-Media -InputPath ./some.mp3 -ReverseAudio |\n  Edit-Media -TargetTime '00:02:59' |\n  Edit-Media  -ShowFrequency -ShowFrequencyMode bar -ShowFrequencyColors '#4488ff', '#224488' |\n  Edit-Media @TriangleRGBAShift\n~~~",
